[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     24[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     25[0m:[38;5;10m[49m For the full pipeline (with Kinesis GPS ingestion, ElastiCache, SageMaker demand forecasting, and Step Functions orchestration), you'd need additional permissions, but this example keeps the focus on the dispatch and coverage optimization logic.
